title: Camp WeWow Weather Week Day 5
description:
It's the last day of Weather Week here at Camp WeWow! Today, we're featuring your camper call-ins around the Camp WeWow campfire! We'll see you back next week with brand new crafts, activties, experiments and more! But until then, head to tinkercast.com/camp to catch up on this week's activities and to print your Weather Week Badge! Then, share what you discovered with us at tinkercast.com/share!
